title: The Fantasy Stock Exchange | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 338)
description:
Adam Humphries, Duke Johnson Jr., and more lead this week's Initial Advice (1:00). Theo Riddick and Cordarrelle Patterson are among the list of players to add off of waivers heading into Week 10 (15:30), and James Conner and Eric Ebron join the group of players to buy low and sell high as the fantasy trade deadline approaches (25:30).
Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
